sequenceDiagram
    actor U as Free User
    participant FE as React<br/>ThreatsPage
    participant API1 as DRF<br/>ThreatListView
    participant API2 as DRF<br/>ThreatCorrelationView
    participant SER as ThreatIntelligenceSerializer
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    U->>FE: Navigate to Threats page
    FE->>API1: GET /api/threats/
    API1->>DB: ThreatIntelligence.objects.all()
    DB-->>API1: QuerySet[ThreatIntelligence]
    API1->>SER: ThreatIntelligenceSerializer(threats, many=True)
    SER-->>API1: Serialized threat data
    API1-->>FE: 200 OK {threats: [...]}
    FE-->>U: Display threat intelligence list
    U->>FE: Click IP to correlate
    FE->>API2: GET /api/threats/{ip}/correlate/
    API2->>DB: ThreatIntelligence.objects.filter(ip=ip)
    API2->>API2: _build_recommendation(threat_data)
    API2-->>FE: 200 OK {correlation, recommendation}
    FE-->>U: Display threat correlation details
